Síoda [sieda]
Pádraic Ó Briain agus Paula Howard
Seán Ó Murchú - a mhaisigh = who ilustrated

Seo í Síoda
Tá sí ag teacht isteach sa teach. = She is comming into the house.
[ta siag cziacht iscziach sa cziach]

Nuair a bhíonn an ghrian ag taitneamh bíonn Síoda amuigh sa ghairdín.
= If the sun is shining, Silk is out in the garden
(nuair=when=an uair=at_the_time (uair=hour=time))[nuer]
(bhíonn= for of "be")
(ghrian=Sun)
(taitneamh=verbal "taitin"=shine + "ag"="ing")[tainef]
(bíonn=bhíonn /see 3 lines above/)
(amuigh=stay outside)[aemo]

Is breá le Síoda luí ar an díon... = Is fine with Síoda to_lie (luí) on the roof
[ys bra le sioda lai ar an dian]
